&lt;h2>Closing thought&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="closing-thought">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#closing-thought" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>A PodDisruptionBudget can govern an eviction, but only replicas, placement, readiness, and tested recovery can make the workload genuinely available.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>